78
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije ruski špion.

79
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,000
[SPEAKER_02] Da, tako je rekao.

80
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:54,000
